metadata.name: SomniPost Christmas NFT 2020
metadata.description: Christmas celebrates the birth of Jesus, who came from God to bring His good message to all people. This Season's Greetings digital postcard is dedicated to Somnium Space community members and serves as a fresh genre of digital art with an avatar and architectural items built on 3944. This digital postcard is stamped with a SomniPost BLOCKMARKE. This NFT by minato.design marks the start of his art & blockchain learning journey.
